						               													<description>Universal Tapestry is a puzzle solitaire game of building a cosmic tapestry with celestial formations.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The player will choose a card from the draw area and it will be placed ortogonally adjacent to other card in the table.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The card placed in the table must comply with two rules:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;- The 4 sides of each card can only be in contact with cards of the same color or with the colors that are adjacent in the rainbow.( red-orange -yellow-green-blue-purple )&amp;#10;&amp;#10;- The symbols of the borders of the card can not be in adjacent contact with the same symbol&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If the card can not be placed then is discarded and another one is drawn .&amp;#10;&amp;#10;There are two modes of playing&amp;#10;&amp;#10;1) By time : Complete the 8x8 matrix as fast as possible.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;2) Discarded cards: Complete the 8x8 matrix avoiding discarding the cards of red and purple colours.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the end of the game if the Matrix is not completed the player loses.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
